    "name": "GlowLinks",
    "description": "This adds a pulsating glow to <a href=\"https://userstyles.org/users/152378\">links</a> when they are hovered or focused.\r\nIt works on Google, Facebook, Tumblr and everywhere else on the web.\r\n12 colours to choose from including a rainbow option.",
    "additionalInfo": "I got the idea from <a href=\"https://userstyles.org/styles/66863/neon-test\">neon test</a> [deleted] by <a href=\"https://userstyles.org/d/users/112647\">wonderlandd</a>. So, a big shout-out to wonderlandd.\r\n\r\nAnd a special thank you to <a href=\"https://userstyles.org/d/users/117864\">hideheader</a> for the RAINBOW.\r\n  \r\n@keyframes",
